        "heading": "Which contractors lead obligations in FY2026 to date?",
        "body": "FISHER SAND & GRAVEL CO leads obligations at $13.3B. TRIWEST HEALTHCARE ALLIANCE CORP follows at $12.6B, with LOCKHEED MARTIN CORPORATION listed at $10B and again at $8.8B. Additional leaders include MCKESSON CORPORATION at $9.9B, ELECTRIC BOAT CORPORATION at $8.3B, and OPTUM PUBLIC SECTOR SOLUTIONS, INC. at $6.6B."
      },
